description: Crêpes Parfait is a mobile unit serving Washington DC authentic French crêpes, in both varieties: sweet and savory. The savory ones, known in France as “Gallettes” are made with rich and hearty buckwheat flour, prepared fresh right before your eyes, the chef spreads the batter over a crêpe griddle, flips it and fills it with a medley of ingredients and serves it to you in a crêpe cone. The other variety is sweet dessert crêpes, made with wheat flour and filled with a variety of aromatic authentic preserves, creams, chocolates and fruits and served to you warm in a crêpes cone.
name: Crepes Parfait
